drm/i915/icl: Define DSI panel programming registers

This patch defines DSI_CMD_RXCTL, DSI_CMD_TXCTL registers,
bitfields, masks and macros used for configuring DSI panel.

v2: Define remaining bitfields

v3 by Jani:
 - Alignment fix

